data.description: This beautiful brick home is nestled on a large lot in a great neighborhood. It's also zoned for the desirable Irmo High School. The attached two-car garage gives you plenty of space for parking & storage. As you enter, you're greeted by handsome wood floors, attractive crown molding, & a spacious floor plan w/ a great flow for entertaining & everyday living. The elegant formal dining room will be perfect for dinners w/ family & friends. The flex room, w/ French Doors, could be used as a formal living room or home office/study. Enjoy cool evenings in front of the cozy gas fireplace in the family room where you'll also find built-in shelving & cabinets & recessed lighting. Located off the family room is a bright sunroom overlooking the backyard. The kitchen boasts recessed lighting, stainless steel appliances, granite counters, an island w/ a breakfast bar, ample cabinet & counter space, & a breakfast/casual dining nook w/ a large bay window. The spacious master bedroom features a sitting room, his-and-hers closets, & a private en suite bathroom w/ a dual vanity & a large walk-in tile shower. The large bonus room over the garage could be used as a 4th bedroom or it would make an excellent game room or entertainment room. The large back deck & fenced-in backyard will be perfect for grilling out, entertaining, or watching the kids play. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, & the interstate. It's also a short drive to Downtown Columbia. Come see your new home, today!
